  - 528
By: Swami Ramdas
---
Mind is a veil that shuts you from the splendour of your immortal
spirit, which is your real being. Tear up this veil by means of
constant meditation and self-surrender. Retire within yourself from
time to time and lose your little ego in the infinite consciousness of
your supreme Self.
